==Production== Under [[Star Cinema]]'s film banner, ''Basta't Kasama Ka'' is director [[Rory B. Quintos]]'s feature film [[directorial debut]] and fellow [[romantic comedy]] film director and colleague [[Cathy Garcia-Molina]] served as the [[assistant director]].<ref name="pep"/> The [[screenplay]] was written by Jerry Lopez Sineneng, Mel Mendoza-Del Rosario, Don Cuaresma and [[Olivia M. Lamasan]], from a story developed by Sineneng and Lamasan.<ref>{{cite news|last1=Mendoza|first1=Abby|title=14 Pinoy Movies for Hopeless Romantics|url=http://www.pep.ph/guide/photos/6567/14-pinoy-movies-for-hopeless-romantics|accessdate=August 3, 2017|work=[[Philippine Entertainment Portal]]|date=April 27, 2015}}</ref>
