The '''Bonnie Bronson Fellowship''', named after American painter and sculptor [[Bonnie Bronson]], is an award presented annually to Pacific Northwest artists.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.lclark.edu/live/news/10657-bonnie-bronson-fellows-20-years|title=Bonnie Bronson Fellows: 20 Years|date=September 7, 2011|accessdate=February 1, 2014|publisher=[[Lewis & Clark College]]}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.reed.edu/reed_magazine/may1997/news/2.html|title= Bronson Collection comes to Reed|accessdate=May 13, 2014|publisher=[[Reed College]]}}</ref>
