{{DISPLAYTITLE:List of ''Kyo Kara Maoh!'' media}}
''[[Kyo Kara Maoh!]]'' is a series of light novels written by [[Tomo Takabayashi]] and illustrated by [[Temari Matsumoto]]. It has been adapted into an [[anime]] and [[manga]] series.

== Light novels ==
Written by Tomo Takabayashi with illustrations by Temari Matsumoto. The first novel was released on November, 2000 and so far there are 22 books in the series.<ref name="Novel Volumes">{{cite web|url=http://www.kadokawa.co.jp/search_plus/index.php?ss=isbn&simple=1&s=4-04-4452&SUBMIT.x=7&SUBMIT.y=12|archive-url=https://archive.is/20120804091054/http://www.kadokawa.co.jp/search_plus/index.php?ss=isbn&simple=1&s=4-04-4452&SUBMIT.x=7&SUBMIT.y=12|dead-url=yes|archive-date=2012-08-04|title=kadokawa Novel|publisher=[[Kadokawa Shoten|Kadokawa]]|language=Japanese|accessdate=2011-09-05}}</ref> 17 are considered to be main story novels and the other 5 are extras and side stories which provide background and other information to the story.

